Pre-Game Insights: The first win must come tonight, at Kauffman Stadium.
Nobody expected to be here. But here they are.
The Royals must win the next two games to keep this remarkable season alive.
Miscellaneous Highlights: One year ago today, the Kansas City Royals were in a very different place than today.
On October 10, 2023, we got some Royals Rumblings reporting on whether or not the Royals would trade Salvador Perez.
Later that day, we asked whether or not the 2023 bullpen was the worst in franchise history.
